    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and has served as a reliable car for its previous owner. The exterior is clean with only a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal road use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is in great shape, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, starts without hesitation, and has a consistent service history. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without needing any immediate work.",
